==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Multum
<hw>Mul"tum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An extract of quassia
licorice, fraudulently used by brewers in order to economize malt and
hops.</def> <rj><au>Craig.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Hard multum</b></col>, <cd>a preparation made from
<spn>Cocculus Indicus</spn>, etc., used to impart an intoxicating
quality to beer.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Multungulate</ent>⟦br⟧
